06-17T06:54:58Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0615/r1673607_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"Why are there hydration breaks at the 2026 World Cup, and why has FIFA been criticised?"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/48945011/why-there-drinks-breaks-2026-world-cup-fifa-criticised"},{"id":49084166,"headline":"What if Reyna's World Cup wonder goal is only the beginning for the USMNT?","byLine":"Sam Borden","description":"Gio Reyna's goal vs. Paraguay felt like a fitting way to end a frustrating four-year chapter of his career. What if it's only the beginning, though?","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0616/r1674230_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:51:55Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0616/r1674230_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"What if Reyna's World Cup wonder goal is only the beginning for the USMNT?"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/49084166/what-gio-reyna-world-cup-wonder-goal-vs-panama-only-beginning-usmnt"},{"id":48709856,"headline":"World Cup 2026: Which players from your Premier League team are going?","byLine":"ESPN","description":"Which Premier League players from your team are representing their country at the 2026 World Cup in the United States, Canada and Mexico?","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0525/r1663354_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:51:08Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0525/r1663354_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"World Cup 2026: Which players from your Premier League team are going?"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/48709856/world-cup-2026-which-players-your-premier-league-team-going"},{"id":48823863,"headline":"Meet England's 2026 World Cup squad: All 26 players picked by Thomas Tuchel and why","byLine":"ESPN","description":"ESPN takes a look at every player named in the England squad for the 2026 World Cup.","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0522/r1661870_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:50:12Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0522/r1661870_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"Meet England's 2026 World Cup squad: All 26 players picked by Thomas Tuchel and why"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/48823863/meet-england-2026-world-cup-squad-26-players-picked-thomas-tuchel-why"},{"id":49090801,"headline":"Harry Souttar is defying all odds -- again -- to star at a World Cup","byLine":"Joey Lynch","description":"In Australia's win over Türkiye, Harry Souttar clocked one of the fastest sprints seen at the World Cup so far. It was an amazing feat given that the Socceroos centre back has barely played in four years.","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0617/r1674669_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:47:00Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0617/r1674669_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"Harry Souttar is defying all odds -- again -- to star at a World Cup"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/49090801/harry-souttar-defying-all-odds-again-star-world-cup"},{"id":48945570,"headline":"Free World Cup 2026 predictor: Simulate your road to the final","byLine":"ESPN","description":"Put your football knowledge to the test with ESPN's free World Cup 2026 predictor games and forecast every twist and turn of the tournament.","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0521/r1661625_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false